<h1>WVARA Field Day Site Directions</h1>
</font>
</center>

<a href="http://www.wvara.org/fd/2002/"><i>[back to the WVARA Field Day 2002 Page]</i></a>
<br>
<a href="http://www.wvara.org/"><i>[back to the WVARA Home Page]</i></a>
<p>

For attendees with GPS navigation, the coordinates of the parking area
at the site are
<ul>
<li>37&deg; 06.147' North latitude
<li>121&deg; 51.852' West longitude
</ul>
<p>

<center>
<table border=1>
<tr><td>
<center>

Users of graphical browsers may select the inset images to view larger images
of important intersections enroute.
